Package fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.lib.nodes

Provides all classes and method to create, manage and edit to disk the ArchiveUnits with their metadata.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArchiveUnit
    Class for SEDA Archive Unit managing metadata, objects, if any, and on disk representation.
    MetadataPerson
    The Class Person.
    MetadataXML
    Abstract class for all kinds of metadata XML representation (XML node, list of XML nodes or string value) This very simple class is aimed to construct and write metadata XML structure.
    MetadataXMLList
    Class for a list of metadata XML representation This very simple class is aimed to construct and write metadata XML structure.
    MetadataXMLNode
    Class for one XML node in metadata with one attribute possibility This very simple class is aimed to construct and write metadata XML structure.
    MetadataXMLString
    Class for a XML string value in metadata This very simple class is aimed to construct and write metadata XML structure.

Package fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.lib.nodes Description

Provides all classes and method to create, manage and edit to disk the ArchiveUnits with their metadata. The metadata is in XML format on disk.
